      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-normal text-gray-900 mb-8 leading-tight max-w-5xl mx-auto hidden" data-lang-id="true">
        Partner Digital Bisnis Anda untuk <span class="relative inline-block">
          <span class="relative z-10 font-bold">Scale Up</span>
          <svg class="absolute -bottom-2 left-0 w-full h-4 z-0" viewBox="0 0 200 20" fill="none">
            <path d="M5 15 Q50 5 95 10 T185 12" stroke="#F59E0B" stroke-width="6" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          </svg>
